into the Jewel City apartments from November 2019 as the first floors of residential development are completed. Upper floors will become available first, moving down the buildings until all floors are finished with Phase 1 completion in April 2020.  Location and Plan <img class="aligncenter wp-image-272901" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-location-2.png" alt="" width="651" height="711" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-location-2.png 533w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-location-2-275x300.png 275w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /><img class="aligncenter wp-image-272815" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City.png" alt="" width="650" height="363" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City.png 1527w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-300x167.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-768x429.png 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-1024x571.png 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Jewel-City-1200x670.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />
